<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>华语沉浸式夏令营 2026</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@400;500;700;900&display=swap');
  :root { --red: #E8391D; --gold: #F5A623; --yellow: #FFD700; --teal: #00B4A6; --dark-teal: #007A70; --sky: #4FC3F7; --light-bg: #E8F8FF; --cream: #FFFBF0; --dark: #1A1A2E; --white: #FFFFFF; --card-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.12); }
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body { font-family: 'Noto Sans SC', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: var(--cream); color: var(--dark); overflow-x: hidden; }
  .navbar { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px); z-index: 1000; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: all 0.3s ease; }
  .navbar.hidden { transform: translateY(-100%); }
  .nav-container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; height: 56px; }
  .nav-logo { font-weight: 900; font-size: 16px; color: var(--red); text-decoration: none; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 4px; list-style: none; }
  .nav-links a { text-decoration: none; color: var(--dark); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 8px; transition: all 0.2s; white-space: nowrap; }
  .nav-links a:hover { background: var(--light-bg); color: var(--teal); }
  .nav-links a.active { background: var(--red); color: white; }
  .nav-toggle { display: none; background: none; border: none; font-size: 24px; cursor: pointer; color: var(--dark); }
  .hero { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E8391D 0%, #FF6B35 40%, #F5A623 100%); padding: 90px 20px 60px; text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .hero::before { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; background: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cg fill='%23ffffff' fill-opacity='0.06'%3E%3Cpath d='M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E"); }
  .hero-badge { display: inline-block; background: var(--yellow); color: var(--dark); font-weight: 900; font-size: 13px; padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 20px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 20px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(36px, 8vw, 72px); font-weight: 900; color: var(--white); line-height: 1.1; text-shadow: 3px 4px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); margin-bottom: 10px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .hero h1 span { color: var(--yellow); }
  .hero-cn { font-size: clamp(18px, 4vw, 28px); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .hero-tagline { font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); margin-bottom: 30px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .hero-stats { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 30px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .hero-stat { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); backdrop-filter: blur(4px); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3); border-radius: 12px; padding: 12px 20px; color: white; text-align: center; }
  .hero-stat strong { display: block; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 900; }
  .hero-stat span { font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.9; }
  .hero-cta { display: inline-block; background: var(--white); color: var(--red); font-size: 16px; font-weight: 900; padding: 14px 36px; border-radius: 40px; text-decoration: none; position: relative; z-index: 1; transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); }
  .hero-cta:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 6px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
  .fade-in { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease; }
  .fade-in.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  section { padding: 60px 20px; }
  .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .section-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 36px; }
  .section-label { background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1.5px; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 4px; }
  .section-title { font-size: clamp(24px, 5vw, 36px); font-weight: 900; color: var(--dark); }
  .dates-band { background: var(--dark); padding: 40px 20px; color: white; }
  .dates-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap: 14px; margin-top: 24px; }
  .date-card { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; transition: all 0.3s ease; }
  .date-card:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .date-num { background: var(--red); color: white; font-weight: 900; font-size: 18px; width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .date-info strong { display: block; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; }
  .date-info span { font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.6; }
  .dates-note { margin-top: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 13px; opacity: 0.6; }
  .highlights { background: var(--light-bg); }
  .highlights-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 16px; }
  .highlight-card { background: white; border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px 20px; box-shadow: var(--card-shadow); border-top: 4px solid var(--teal); text-align: center; transition: all 0.3s ease; }
  .highlight-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); }
  .highlight-card .icon { font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .highlight-card h3 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 6px; color: var(--dark); }
  .highlight-card p { font-size: 13px; color: #666; line-height: 1.6; }
  .dimensions { background: white; }
  .dim-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
  .dim-item { display: flex; gap: 18px; align-items: flex-start; background: var(--light-bg); border-radius: 14px; padding: 20px 24px; border-left: 5px solid var(--teal); transition: all 0.3s ease; }
  .dim-item:hover { box-shadow: var(--card-shadow); transform: translateX(4px); }
  .dim-num { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--red), var(--gold)); color: white; font-weight: 900; font-size: 22px; width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(232,57,29,0.3); }
  .dim-content h3 { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .dim-content p { font-size: 14px; color: #555; line-height: 1.65; }
  .schedule { background: var(--light-bg); }
  .schedule-table-wrap { overflow-x: auto; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: var(--card-shadow); }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; background: white; min-width: 680px; font-size: 13px; }
  thead tr { background: var(--dark); color: white; }
  thead th { padding: 14px 10px; font-weight: 800; text-align: center; font-size: 13px; }
  thead th:first-child { background: var(--red); border-radius: 16px 0 0 0; }
  tbody tr:nth-child(even) { background: #F5FFFE; }
  tbody td { padding: 10px 10px; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; line-height: 1.5; }
  tbody td:first-child { font-weight: 800; background: var(--dark); color: white; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
  .cell-highlight { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFF3E0, #FFE0B2) !important; font-weight: 700; color: #E65100; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 12px; }
  .cell-fixed { background: #E8F8FF !important; font-size: 12px; color: #555; }
  .schedule-note { margin-top: 16px; font-size: 12px; color: #888; text-align: center; }
  .living { background: var(--light-bg); }
  .living-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; }
  .living-card { background: white; border-radius: 16px; padding: 28px 24px; box-shadow: var(--card-shadow); transition: all 0.3s ease; }
  .living-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); }
  .living-card .l-icon { font-size: 40px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .living-card h3 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .living-card p { font-size: 13px; color: #666; line-height: 1.7; }
  .activity-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; margin-top: 10px; }
  .activity-tag { background: #E8F8FF; color: var(--dark-teal); font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 20px; }
  .goals { background: white; }
  .goals-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .goal-card { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--light-bg), white); border-radius: 16px; padding: 28px 24px; border: 2px solid #E0F4FF; position: relative; overflow: hidden; transition: all 0.3s ease; }
  .goal-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); }
  .goal-card::before { content: attr(data-num); position: absolute; top: -10px; right: 12px; font-size: 80px; font-weight: 900; color: rgba(0,180,166,0.08); line-height: 1; }
  .goal-card .g-icon { font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .goal-card h3 { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .goal-card p { font-size: 13px; color: #666; line-height: 1.7; }
  .honor-strip { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--red), var(--gold)); border-radius: 16px; padding: 30px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; color: white; text-align: center; }
  .honor-item { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; }
  .honor-item strong { display: block; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 900; }
  .honor-sep { font-size: 24px; opacity: 0.4; }
  .faq { background: var(--light-bg); }
  .faq-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
  .faq-item { background: white; border-radius: 14px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); transition: all 0.3s ease; }
  .faq-item:hover { box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
  .faq-q { padding: 18px 22px; font-weight: 800; font-size: 15px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; cursor: pointer; user-select: none; transition: background 0.2s; }
  .faq-q:hover { background: var(--light-bg); }
  .faq-q::after { content: '▼'; margin-left: auto; font-size: 12px; color: var(--teal); transition: transform 0.3s; }
  .faq-item.open .faq-q::after { transform: rotate(180deg); }
  .faq-num { background: var(--red); color: white; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 900; width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .faq-a { padding: 0 22px 0 62px; font-size: 14px; color: #555; line-height: 1.7; max-height: 0; overflow: hidden; transition: max-height 0.4s ease, padding 0.4s ease; }
  .faq-item.open .faq-a { padding: 0 22px 18px 62px; max-height: 500px; }
  .packing { background: white; }
  .pack-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .pack-cat { background: var(--light-bg); border-radius: 14px; padding: 20px 18px; }
  .pack-cat h4 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; color: var(--dark-teal); }
  .pack-cat ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .pack-cat ul li { font-size: 13px; color: #555; padding: 5px 0; border-bottom: 1px dashed #ddd; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
  .pack-cat ul li::before { content: '✓'; color: var(--teal); font-weight: 800; font-size: 12px; }
  .tips-box { background: #FFF8E1; border-left: 4px solid var(--gold); border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0; padding: 20px 24px; }
  .tips-box h4 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--dark); margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .tips-box ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .tips-box ul li { font-size: 13px; color: #555; padding: 5px 0; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 8px; }
  .tips-box ul li::before { content: '●'; color: var(--gold); font-size: 8px; margin-top: 5px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .registration { background: var(--dark); color: white; }
  .reg-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 24px; }
  .reg-box { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border-radius: 14px; padding: 24px; }
  .reg-box h4 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 14px; color: var(--gold); }
  .reg-box ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .reg-box ul li { font-size: 13px; padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); line-height: 1.6; }
  .reg-box ul li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .reg-box ul li strong { color: var(--sky); }
  .contact-cta { margin-top: 32px; text-align: center; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--red), var(--gold)); border-radius: 16px; padding: 30px; }
  .contact-cta h3 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 900; color: white; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .contact-cta p { font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .contact-btn { display: inline-block; background: white; color: var(--red); font-size: 16px; font-weight: 900; padding: 12px 32px; border-radius: 40px; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s; }
  .contact-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); }
  .back-to-top { position: fixed; bottom: 24px; right: 24px; width: 48px; height: 48px; background: var(--red); color: white; border: none; border-radius: 50%; font-size: 20px; cursor: pointer; box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(232,57,29,0.4); opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition: all 0.3s ease; z-index: 999; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
  .back-to-top.show { opacity: 1; visibility: visible; }
  .back-to-top:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(232,57,29,0.5); }
  footer { background: #111; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45); text-align: center; padding: 24px 20px; font-size: 12px; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .nav-links { display: none; } .nav-toggle { display: block; } .nav-links.show { display: flex; flex-direction: column; position: absolute; top: 56px; left: 0; right: 0; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.98); padding: 16px 20px; gap: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); } .hero { padding: 80px 16px 50px; } .hero-stats { gap: 8px; } .hero-stat { padding: 10px 14px; } .hero-stat strong { font-size: 18px; } section { padding: 40px 16px; } .dim-item { flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; } .dim-num { width: 40px; height: 40px; font-size: 18px; } .schedule-table-wrap { margin: 0 -8px; border-radius: 12px; } table { font-size: 12px; min-width: 600px; } thead th, tbody td { padding: 8px 6px; } .honor-strip { flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; } .honor-sep { display: none; } }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<<nav class="navbar" id="navbar">
  <div class="nav-container">
    <a href="#" class="nav-logo">🔥 华语夏令营</a>
    <button class="nav-toggle" id="navToggle">☰</button>
    <ul class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
      <li><a href="#dates">营期</a></li>
      <li><a href="#highlights">亮点</a></li>
      <li><a href="#dimensions">赋能</a></li>
      <li><a href="#schedule">课表</a></li>
      <li><a href="#living">生活</a></li>
      <li><a href="#goals">目标</a></li>
      <li><a href="#faq">FAQ</a></li>
      <li><a href="#packing">准备</a></li>
      <li><a href="#register">报名</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</nav>
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-badge">🌏 东南亚 · 2026 夏季</div>
  <h1>趣味学习 <span>华语</span></h1>
  <div class="hero-cn">放纵一夏 · 华语夏令营</div>
  <p class="hero-tagline">5天4夜 · 沉浸式营地 · 双语环境 · 7-13岁</p>
  <div class="hero-stats">
    <div class="hero-stat"><strong>24/7</strong><span>华语浸润</span></div>
    <div class="hero-stat"><strong>1 : 5</strong><span>师生配比</span></div>
    <div class="hero-stat"><strong>7-13</strong><span>年龄范围</span></div>
    <div class="hero-stat"><strong>25+</strong><span>每期最少人数</span></div>
  </div>
  <a href="#register" class="hero-cta">立即了解报名 →</a>
</div>
<div class="dates-band" id="dates">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header" style="margin-bottom:0;">
      <span class="section-label" style="background:var(--teal);">📅 日期</span>
      <h2 class="section-title" style="color:white;">2026 营期安排</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="dates-grid">
      <div class="date-card fade-in"><div class="date-num">1</div><div class="date-info"><strong>7月04日 – 7月08日</strong><span>第一期</span></div></div>
      <div class="date-card fade-in"><div class="date-num">2</div><div class="date-info"><strong>7月12日 – 7月16日</strong><span>第二期</span></div></div>
      <div class="date-card fade-in"><div class="date-num">3</div><div class="date-info"><strong>7月19日 – 7月23日</strong><span>第三期</span></div></div>
      <div class="date-card fade-in"><div class="date-num">4</div><div class="date-info"><strong>7月26日 – 7月30日</strong><span>第四期</span></div></div>
      <div class="date-card fade-in"><div class="date-num">5</div><div class="date-info"><strong>8月02日 – 8月06日</strong><span>第五期</span></div></div>
      <div class="date-card fade-in"><div class="date-num">6</div><div class="date-info"><strong>8月09日 – 8月13日</strong><span>第六期</span></div></div>
    </div>
    <p class="dates-note">每期需满25人方可开营 · 乡村自然教育基地</p>
  </div>
</div>
<section class="highlights" id="highlights">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-label">✨ 亮点</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">营地亮点</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="highlights-grid">
      <div class="highlight-card fade-in">
        <div class="icon">🗣️</div>
        <h3>24小时华语浸润</h3>
        <p>母语为中文的老师全程陪伴——从课堂到餐桌——打破"沉默华语"的壁垒！</p>
      </div>
      <div class="highlight-card fade-in">
        <div class="icon">🌾</div>
        <h3>田园自然教育营地</h3>
        <p>在真实的乡村环境中通过动手实践学习华语——采茶、陶艺、捕鱼等。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="highlight-card fade-in">
        <div class="icon">🏠</div>
        <h3>暑假一站式托管</h3>
        <p>作业辅导 + 体能活动 + 户外探索 + STEM手工。一站式暑期解决方案！</p>
      </div>
      <div class="highlight-card fade-in">
        <div class="icon">🛡️</div>
        <h3>多维保障体系</h3>
        <p>获奖住宿 + 营养均衡膳食 + 24小时经验丰富的员工看护。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="dimensions" id="dimensions">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-label">🌟 框架</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">五维赋能全面成长</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="dim-list">
      <div class="dim-item fade-in">
        <div class="dim-num">1</div>
        <div class="dim-content">
          <h3>实战华语能力</h3>
          <p>母语为中文的老师全天候引导对话、角色扮演和情境课堂活动——让华语从课本走进生活。营员们学会用华语点餐、问路、交朋友，还能登台表演！</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="dim-item fade-in">
        <div class="dim-num">2</div>
        <div class="dim-content">
          <h3>成长导向陪护</h3>
          <p>作业辅导 + 日常生活管理 + 安全保障。家长放心，孩子培养独立性——全都在安全、结构化的华语环境中进行。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="dim-item fade-in">
        <div class="dim-num">3</div>
        <div class="dim-content">
          <h3>多元文化素养</h3>
